var(--space-2)`, the 18 px nav-item icon lands at viewport x ≈ 29
(rail centre = 30) and the 16 px footer-button icon at viewport x ≈ 36 —
both visually centred inside the visible rail.

Refresh the `.nav-list` / `.sidebar-footer` counter-transform comment and
add a comment on the collapsed `.nav-item` rule documenting the
`left center` origin / identity-composition relationship so the next
edit doesn't reintroduce centred icons.

